---
const walkthroughHref = "/schedule-a-walkthrough/";
---

<section class="section dark final-cta" id="early-access">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-main animate-fade-up">
      <div class="cta-content-holder">
        <div class="cta-content">
          <p class="subtitle">READY FOR MARKETING THAT KEEPS IMPROVING?</p>
          <h2>Stop chasing every new marketing tool.<br />Build the system that gets better with them.</h2>
          <p class="cta-description">
            New tools will keep arriving. The advantage is not trying everything — it is having one marketing system that learns your business, organizes your campaigns, remembers approvals, and improves as better capabilities become useful.
          </p>
          <div class="button-group">
            <a href={walkthroughHref} class="button">Book a Walkthrough</a>
            <a href="/#how-it-works" class="button is-secondary">See How It Works</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="cta-image-holder animate-scale-in">
        <img src="/images/cta-stone.avif" alt="Markethink guided system preview" class="cta-image animate-parallax" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .final-cta {
    padding: 8rem 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cta-main {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .cta-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .cta-description {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.68);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 34rem;
  }

  .button-group {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cta-image-holder {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .cta-image {
    max-width: 100%;
    border-radius: var(--radius-medium);
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .final-cta {
      padding: 4rem 0;
    }

    .cta-main {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .cta-content {
      align-items: center;
    }

    .button-group {
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .cta-image-holder {
      order: -1;
    }
  }
</style>
